</paragraph>
</caption>
<paragraph blockId="16.[151,1437,151,964]" pageId="16" pageNumber="79">
<emphasis box="[199,403,330,355]" italics="true" pageId="16" pageNumber="79">Surface sculpture:</emphasis>
All legs with fine dense punctures. T1 with sparse fine shallow punctures except impunctate on basal depression; metasomal sterna with coarse shallow crowded punctures intermixed with sparse coarse punctures.
</paragraph>
